sml-mode (3.9.5-10) unstable; urgency=low

  * Changed priority back to optional and Build-Depends-Indep to
    Build-Depends.
  * Converted to using dpatch.
  * Applied patch from Sebastian Schaffert to fix xemacs problem when
    sending the buffer contents to the interpreter. Part of bug#274266.
  * Included a watch file.
    
 -- Jens Peter Secher <jps@debian.org>  Sun, 10 Oct 2004 00:29:58 +0200

